{"tid":556464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士車禍現場，當年曾發生28人意外死亡慘劇，有「猛鬼橋」之稱","createTime":"2018-02-10T13:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T14:18:04.000Z","uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1b67500dc7883f7285480ba080c6fde682ec2482","tid":556464,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:22:16.000Z","msg":"大埔公路傍晚發生19死大車禍，現場為大埔松仔園，其得名有指因港府於上世紀20年代於該處廣植樹木，其中主要為馬尾松，故被稱松仔園。其實上址過去亦曾發生嚴重意外，當中最嚴重是1955年8月28日，當時一批小學生到上址旅行時遇山洪暴發，眾人躲於橋下避雨，最終意外導致28人罹難，之後發生意外的木橋屢傳鬼話，更被稱「猛鬼橋」。<br />\n<br />\n1955年8月28日，一批來自多間小學的學生及九廣鐵路員工親屬到大埔松仔園郊遊，原本天朗氣清，但午後暴雨掩至，眾人躲於橋下避雨，詎料山洪暴發，眾人走避不及，部分更被沖至30多尺下蜜月潭，28人全部喪命。<br />\n<br />\n當時報章形容死者「均屬焦頭爛額，全身傷痕，其中多名血肉模糊」，並以「屍如山積，慘不忍睹」來形這場慘劇，其後該處衍生出不少鬧鬼傳說，該橋亦被稱為「猛鬼橋」。紀念事件的《怒水橋洪流肇禍記》石碑一度豎立在大埔七約鄉公所，其後重置於「大埔滘自然護理區」入口附近的大埔滘花園。該地附近傳出不少鬧鬼事件，有指不少的士司機在松仔園一帶遇上小童截車，當的士接截小童半途後，小童便在車廂中消失。"},{"pid":"fdde546b7bb46da95901e60dd0ea6a3d2f9ca8d1","tid":556464,"uid":158283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:25:44.000Z","msg":"幾十年前啦"},{"pid":"4feb6fc4c30941b857b8f5a31a5b64587a8b9d4f","tid":556464,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:25:45.000Z","msg":"細細個已經聽過「猛鬼橋」鬼故"},{"pid":"aed7f4119c9611b26e5824275d617a68dcc6a0d5","tid":556464,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"60年後先搵到替身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有9個未搵"},{"pid":"03fec0c7864974a8946702ae6f65a93abb3bfc56","tid":556464,"uid":165965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:36:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/fbia/bkn/cnt/fbia/20171209/fbia-20171209155201217-1209_31011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Ffbia%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffbia%2F20171209%2Ffbia-20171209155201217-1209_31011_001.html&d=mnHpIPXg%2BssSCV9o%2BYI3CTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=28c91e1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/fbia/bkn/cnt/fbia/20171209/fbia-20171209155201217-1209_31011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n我睇完好L心寒"},{"pid":"3c695d8693ce7139fbc2a5cb1f34a2bebe1783f9","tid":556464,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8cda51057e93755275a4294563e91a5e5ab838","tid":556464,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03fec0c7864974a8946702ae6f65a93abb3bfc56","tid":556464,"uid":165965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:36:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/fbia/bkn/cnt/fbia/20171209/fbia-20171209155201217-1209_31011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Ffbia%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffbia%2F20171209%2Ffbia-20171209155201217-1209_31011_001.html&d=mnHpIPXg%2BssSCV9o%2BYI3CTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=28c91e1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/fbia/bkn/cnt/fbia/20171209/fbia-20171209155201217-1209_31011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n我睇完好L心寒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冤魂搵替死鬼　向路過車輛招手</span><br />\n<br />\n自此猛鬼橋便傳出有冤魂向路過車輛招手搵替死鬼，該處亦成為交通黑點，不時有人枉死於車禍意外。山洪暴發意外後一年，一輛行經該處的運菜貨車翻落數百呎下山腳，釀成6死8傷的交通慘劇。1999年，一名24歲司機在猛鬼橋失事，私家車着火將司機活活燒死。2013年，一名男子駕駛迷你開篷車在同一彎位失控撞破鐵欄，翻滾落山坡翻側，大樹壓向原為車頂位置，但因屬開篷車，他得以逃過被壓扁一劫，大樹僅橫擱於面前，頭部受傷送院後情況嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n傳聞有不少司機親眼看見在松仔園一帶遇上小童截車，當有好心人把小童接上車後，過了不久便會發現小童在車廂中消失，村民直指有厲鬼作弄司機；亦有司機午夜在現場接載4名男女到粉嶺後，落車竟然不見人形。"},{"pid":"7aa9d57f8d3fb347c9cfbcd4e9c8f0bd1d3a1416","tid":556464,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c695d8693ce7139fbc2a5cb1f34a2bebe1783f9","tid":556464,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:42:43.000Z","msg":"死人黎抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9702b4453d7298fbe6b7b2d65b823b6d219ecada","tid":556464,"uid":129378,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:42:47.000Z","msg":"真係呢個位咩？<br />\n宜家果到係大埔尾，同松仔園有小小距離。"},{"pid":"4e2bdf5448f227b4dfb7f4d4b996ab0cf94dde60","tid":556464,"uid":11868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:43:18.000Z","msg":"今次單野果度唔係松仔園，d報紙佬亂狗咁黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe119e2d2d8bf1e0dbc002dc3032aa3726b6d79","tid":556464,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:46:53.000Z","msg":"成日以為洪水橋叫猛鬼橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5026401359820621bd1eff6e7f622e446b4c6b28","tid":556464,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e2bdf5448f227b4dfb7f4d4b996ab0cf94dde60","tid":556464,"uid":11868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:43:18.000Z","msg":"今次單野果度唔係松仔園，d報紙佬亂狗咁黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:50:59.000Z","msg":"松仔園鄰近九廣鐵路大埔滘站及大埔公路 ，交通方便，而且兩邊山峰綠樹成蔭，中央連綿數公里長的河溪水澗，當年闊約15米，可供行山漫步、野餐、游泳等活動，成為郊遊的熱門地點。<br />\n<br />\n在1955年8月28日的下午約1時30分，一群師生正在溪澗旁午膳，突然下雨，他們走到橋樑的底部避雨，誰知山洪突至，大部分人走避不及，被洪水沖走，遇難者經過大水渠（現為滌濤山）再被沖出大海。事後點算，一共28人罹難，死者中約20人是在聖雅各學校就讀。事後大埔七約鄉公所立《怒水橋洪流肇禍記》石碑以誌此慘劇[2]。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%80%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%2588%25A5%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C&d=mnHpIPXg%2BssSCV9o%2BYI3CTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=9dc34749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%80%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C</a>"},{"pid":"860973708c8d66ac765aa03345fe4ec3320d4c88","tid":556464,"uid":137921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T14:12:16.000Z","msg":"我師父話.jpg"},{"pid":"28d6a412bcf357288e3a8827cb6d2ce82cca47fc","tid":556464,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T14:17:42.000Z","msg":"大埔公路好多「喃無阿尼托佛」碑"},{"pid":"5ff2b341ea821ad4b150c2cfe530304f76bdf2eb","tid":556464,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T14:18:04.000Z","msg":"猛鬼橋 我細細個就聽過呢個名"}]}